songs.title: Phsycosis
songs.lyrics:
[Chorus]
I'm sufferin' from psychosis
I can see that you see, but you won't leave me alone
Psychosis
Voices in my head, I'd rather be dead
It's psychosis

[Post-Chorus]
The child with many disorders in his head
Unlike everybody else
That's why nobody helps him, at all
He just did it by hisself

[Verse 1]
Nobody ever understands me
Psychosis runnin' through my head
Ah, psychosis
Oh, oh, psychosis

[Chorus]
I'm sufferin' from psychosis
I can see that you see, but you won't leave me alone
Psychosis
Voices in my head, I'd rather be dead
I'm sufferin' from psychosis
I can see that you see, but you won't leave me alone
Psychosis
Voices in my head, I'd rather be dead
It's psychosis

[Verse 2: ?]
Said it once I'll say it again
My life is coming to the end
Those people left that were my friends
Who thought I cared, but I pretend
This is now and that was then
I never [?] it can't happen
[?] I'm left in
What the hell is going on?
[?] where I went wrong
Well, well I'll be strong
Woah, [?]
Woah, woah, [?]

[Chorus]
I'm sufferin' from psychosis
I can see that you see, but you won't leave me alone
Psychosis
Voices in my head, I'd rather be dead
I'm sufferin' from psychosis
I can see that you see, but you won't leave me alone
Psychosis
Voices in my head, I'd rather be dead
It's psychosis

[Verse 3: ?]
I see you
You don't see me comin' from behind to kill you
I see you
You better run cause I'm comin' from behind to slit your throat
I'm coming for you!

[Chorus]
I'm sufferin' from psychosis
I can see that you see, but you won't leave me alone
Psychosis
Voices in my head, I'd rather be dead
It's psychosis

[Outro: ?]
All of us, all of us, all of us, all of us
All of us, all of us, all of us, all of us
All of us have it in us
I'm talkin' 'bout psychosis
